ing for me."]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[100]},{"code":213,"indent":0,"parameters":[7,8,true]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Knight"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Yo there, [Nice to meet you]... I guess."]},{"code":357,"indent":0,"parameters":["TRP_SkitMZ","slideIn","[登場]slideIn/スライドイン",{"name":"Shino","wait":"def","position":"6","slideLength":"def","speed":"def","direction":"auto","easeType":"def","pushIn":"def"}]},{"code":657,"indent":0,"parameters":["キャラ名 = Shino"]},{"code":657,"indent":0,"parameters":["ウェイト = def"]},{"code":657,"indent":0,"parameters":["位置 = 6"]},{"code":657,"indent":0,"parameters":["スライド距離 = def"]},{"code":657,"indent":0,"parameters":["スライドスピード = def"]},{"code":657,"indent":0,"parameters":["スライド方向。 = auto"]},{"code":657,"indent":0,"parameters":["イージング = def"]},{"code":657,"indent":0,"parameters":["プッシュイン = def"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\SE[18]Yeah... Nice to meet you too, Knight-chan."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["A familiar voice, from a face I've never seen before. The imbalanced"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["nature of that feeling made me forget about my daily life, and I felt like"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I'd just walked into a fantasy world."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["A character-print t-shirt, and a jacket of a subdued color."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I couldn't call him stylish even as flattery... but that also"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["made me just as relieved."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["He'd told me on the phone before, that since he's an otaku"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["and a shut-in, he's never really talked to a girl before."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["With my eyes, I could tell that his words until now were the truth."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["...Which meant that--"]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\se[55-nb]That illness you mentioned... you really do have it, huh?"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Knight"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Yeah, just as I said, I don't think I've got that much time."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\SE[54-nb]I see... I'm sorry."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Knight"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Thanks for believing me. Forgive me, for asking you to do"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["something in a place like this."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\se[20-nb]No, it's fine. You sure you're... fine with it being me?"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\SE[14]You know, the person you want to... spend your precious remaining time with?"]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I'm sure that in the future, I'll forever walk side by side with \\n[1]."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["But, this person... this friend of mine, who's been nothing but nice to me,"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["if I let this chance go, it'll be gone forever."]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[100]},{"code":213,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,8,false]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\se[21]......."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["It was at this point, that I realized."]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["My actions up until now weren't motivated by justice or love or anything like that."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["Exhibitionism, a superiority complex, a sense of accomplishment "]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["over it being something only I could do. Such dark emotions lying"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["dormant within me were the reason why I was 'serving' him like this."]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I couldn't just walk away from this story,"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["when it was my selfish actions that caused it to start."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Knight"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["My time limit is... two weeks."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[98]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I'd already decided to pollute my heart,"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["to hear and listen to his final request."]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[96]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\SE[54-nb]Knight-chan, I'm sorry. It's my... first time so,"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["I don't know if I'll be able to do it properly but--"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,2,2,"Shino"]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\se[63-nb]I'll do my best so... tell me, what you want me to do?"]},{"code":242,"indent":0,"parameters":[2]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[100]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"blace",0,0,0,0,100,100,0,0]},{"code":